CONSUMER_CONTRACT_MANAGER_API_KEY: test

PROVIDER_CONTRACT_MANAGER_ENDPOINT: http://provider-contract-manager-mock:8080/contract/v1/
PROVIDER_CONTRACT_MANAGER_API_KEY: test